Package: vecaniso
Title: Fit spatiotemporal models with anisotropy based on vector fields
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Best",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jkbest@uw.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8920-0900"))
Maintainer: John Best <jkbest@uw.edu>
Description: This package fits spatiotemporal models with spatially varying anisotropy. The degree and direction of anisotropy is defined by a pre- specified vector field. The package also includes some facilities for deriving vector fields.
